1114
01:05:48,320 --> 01:05:51,680
- I have to go.
- No, don't. Please. No, no.
Listen to me. Come on.

1115
01:05:51,760 --> 01:05:53,840
Whatever it is-- Come on.
You can tell me.

1116
01:05:53,920 --> 01:05:56,240
- I can help you. I swear I can.
- Good night. I'll see you tomorrow.

1117
01:05:56,320 --> 01:05:59,240
Please, let me help you.

1118
01:05:59,320 --> 01:06:02,160
