1123
01:06:27,600 --> 01:06:30,440
Larry's been in and out of
the E.R. for a couple of years.

1124
01:06:30,480 --> 01:06:33,640
- Not because he's accident-prone.
- No. His father died two years ago.

1125
01:06:33,680 --> 01:06:36,760
