and return these.

1507
01:35:22,560 --> 01:35:24,280
[ Softly ]
Yeah.

1508
01:35:24,360 --> 01:35:27,680
And get a suit.

1509
01:35:30,080 --> 01:35:31,440
[ Murmuring ]

1510
01:35:31,440 --> 01:35:32,440
[ Murmuring ]

1511
01:35:51,040 --> 01:35:52,920
[ Man ]
Hunter Adams.

1512
01:35:55,240 --> 01:35:58,360
You've been accused of
practicing medicine without a license.

1513
01:35:58,440 --> 01:36:00,640
That's a very
grave charge, son.

1514
01:36:00,720 --> 01:36:05,120
Are you aware that it's unlawful
to practice medicine without
a medical license ?

1515
01:36:05,200 --> 01:36:06,800
Yes, sir, I am.

1516
01:36:06,880 --> 01:36:10,520
Are you aware that running a medical
clinic without the proper licensing...

1517
01:36:10,600 --> 01:36:12,760
can place both you
and the public...

1518
01:36:12,840 --> 01:36:14,840
in a great deal of danger ?

1519
01:36:14,920 --> 01:36:16,800
Is a home a clinic, sir ?

1520
01:36:16,880 --> 01:36:19,880
If you are admitting patients
and treating them...

1521
01:36:19,960 --> 01:36:22,320
physical location
is irrelevant.

1522
01:36:22,400 --> 01:36:26,000
Sir, will you define
treatment for me ?

1523
01:36:26,080 --> 01:36:30,640
Yes. Treatment would be defined
as the care of a patient
seeking medical attention.

1524
01:36:31,800 --> 01:36:34,960
Have you been treating patients,
Mr. Adams ?

1525
01:36:35,040 --> 01:36:37,880
