whatever help I can.

1527
01:36:39,880 --> 01:36:41,880
Mr. Adams...

1528
01:36:41,920 --> 01:36:45,880
have you or have you not
been treating patients at your ranch ?

1529
01:36:47,840 --> 01:36:51,120
Everyone who comes to the ranch
is a patient, yes.

1530
01:36:51,200 --> 01:36:53,920
[ Murmuring ]

1531
01:36:54,000 --> 01:36:57,120
And every person who comes
to the ranch is also a doctor.

1532
01:36:59,040 --> 01:37:01,200
I'm sorry ?

1533
01:37:01,280 --> 01:37:03,680
Every person who comes
to the ranch is in need...

1534
01:37:03,760 --> 01:37:06,360
of some form of physical
or mental help.

1535
01:37:06,440 --> 01:37:08,320
They're patients.

1536
01:37:08,360 --> 01:37:13,520
But also every person who comes
to the ranch is in charge of
taking care of someone else--

1537
01:37:13,600 --> 01:37:15,480
whether it's cooking for them,
cleaning them...

1538
01:37:15,520 --> 01:37:18,320
or even as simple a task
as listening.

1539
01:37:18,400 --> 01:37:20,240
That makes them doctors.

1540
01:37:20,320 --> 01:37:25,400
I use that term broadly, but is not a
doctor someone who helps someone else ?

1541
01:37:25,440 --> 01:37:29,400
When did the term "doctor" get
treated with such reverence, as,
"Right this way, Doctor Smith"...

1542
01:37:29,480 --> 01:37:32,320
