what wonderful footpads"...

1543
01:37:32,360 --> 01:37:35,920
or, "Pardon me, Dr. Patterson,
but your flatulence has no odor" ?

1544
01:37:36,000 --> 01:37:38,480
[ Laughing, Murmuring ]

1545
01:37:38,560 --> 01:37:41,960
