your door to those in need--

1549
01:37:52,320 --> 01:37:54,560
those in pain--

1550
01:37:54,640 --> 01:37:59,800
caring for them, listening
to them, applying a cold cloth
until a fever breaks--

1551
01:37:59,880 --> 01:38:02,080
if this is practicing medicine,
if this is treating a patient...

1552
01:38:02,160 --> 01:38:04,600
then I am guilty
as charged, sir.

1553
01:38:04,680 --> 01:38:08,120
Did you consider the ramifications
of your actions ?

1554
01:38:08,200 --> 01:38:10,400
