maybe even humor ?

1559
01:38:21,000 --> 01:38:22,880
Death is not the enemy,
gentlemen.

1560
01:38:22,920 --> 01:38:25,760
If we're gonna fight a disease,
let's fight one of the most
terrible diseases of all--

1561
01:38:25,800 --> 01:38:27,680
indifference.

1562
01:38:27,720 --> 01:38:31,640
Now, I've sat in your schools and heard
people lecture on transference...

1563
01:38:31,680 --> 01:38:33,560
and professional distance.

1564
01:38:33,600 --> 01:38:36,000
Transference
is inevitable, sir.

1565
01:38:36,080 --> 01:38:38,480
Every human being
has an impact on another.

1566
01:38:38,560 --> 01:38:41,880
Why don't we want that in
a patient/doctor relationship ?

1567
01:38:41,960 --> 01:38:46,200
That's why I've listened to your
teachings, and I believe they're wrong.

1568
01:38:46,240 --> 01:38:50,000
